PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA cat saved by the RSPCA during a five-
OL,8,Fhour rescue mission in Portsmouth has
OL,9,Fbeen reunited with his owner almost
OL,10,Ffour years after going missing.
OL,12,F10-year-old Alfie disappeared in July
OL,13,F2022, shortly after owner Mandy Davis
OL,14,Fhad moved house.
OL,16,FShe'd given up hope of seeing him
OL,17,Fagain, until the efforts of the
OL,18,FRSPCA's rescue team.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAnimal Rescue Officer Sarah Whatton
OL,8,Fwas called to Madeira Road in
OL,9,FPortsmouth on 15 March 2026 to reports
OL,10,Fof a cat stuck in a small 10cm gap
OL,11,Fbetween two brick conservatories.
OL,13,FDespite Sarah's best efforts, she
OL,14,Fneeded to call in help from both an
OL,15,FRSPCA colleague and Hampshire Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAfter five hours, 10-year-old Alfie
OL,8,Fwas successfully released, before his
OL,9,Frescuers realised he was in fact
OL,10,Fmicrochipped and were soon able to
OL,11,Freunite him with his delighted owner
OL,12,FMandy.
OL,14,FMandy said: "I couldn't quite believe
OL,15,Fit when the RSPCA called to tell me
OL,16,Fthey had him, and he'd been found just
OL,17,Ftwo roads away from our house!
OL,19,F"It still feels like a bit of a blur;
OL,20,FI honestly didn't think I'd ever see
OL,21,Fhim again."
OL,26,@vD@MOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAnimal Rescue Officer Sarah Whatton
OL,8,Fsaid: "We were concerned about the cat
OL,9,Fbecause the caller said he was last
OL,10,Fseen at around 3am, so he could have
OL,11,Fbeen stuck in the gap for some time.
OL,12,FDespite this, he was bright and alert.
OL,14,F"We think he'd fallen from a first
OL,15,Ffloor roof and got stuck in a tight
OL,16,F10cm (4in) gap between two brick
OL,17,Fconservatories."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FCatherine Edwards, who lived in the
OL,8,Fhome near where Alfie was stuck, said:
OL,9,F"I was in bed but could see my
OL,10,Fneighbour in my garden peering down
OL,11,Fthe side of the houses so went out to
OL,12,Fsee what was going on.
OL,14,F"The cat had been straying in the area
OL,15,Ffor some time and regularly visited
OL,16,Four garden; our neighbour was feeding
OL,17,Fhim."
OL,19,F"He was so far in and the gap was so
OL,20,Ftiny, there was no way I could reach
OL,21,Fhim so I called the RSPCA for help."
OL,26,@qD@AOU{D@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FWith the light fading, the RSPCA
OL,8,Fofficers called a local vet who
OL,9,Fsedated Alfie to enable the rescue and
OL,10,Fminimise his distress.
OL,12,FHis rescuers made a special
OL,13,Fcontraption so they could safely
OL,14,Fadminister the injection in such a
OL,15,Fconfined space.
OL,17,FEven at that point, time was of the
OL,18,Fessence to make sure the process
OL,19,Fhappened safely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FFellow RSPCA Animal Rescue Officer
OL,8,FMorgan Ellison said: "The vet told us
OL,9,Fonce the sedation took effect we had
OL,10,Fone minute to free him before there
OL,11,Fwas serious risk of breathing
OL,12,Fdifficulties so we were really up
OL,13,Fagainst the clock.
OL,15,F"We were concerned about injuring him
OL,16,Fbut we'd run out of other options.
OL,18,F"It took all three of us to pull him
OL,19,Fout and by some absolute miracle he
OL,20,Fcame out unharmed."
OL,26,@pD@VOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775131865
OL,3,CCat saved during five-hour rescue
OL,4,Cmission reunited with owner after four
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAlfie is now recovering well back at
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,FSince June 2024, it has been a legal
OL,11,Frequirement in England for owned cats
OL,12,Fover 20 weeks to be microchipped.
OL,14,FThe RSPCA have also advised that
OL,15,Fmicrochipping is the best way to
OL,16,Fensure that cats can be reunited with
OL,17,Fowners if they are lost or stolen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
